STEPS TO CREATE A FLASK APP 

1. make directory
2. define app.py inside that directory 
3. import all basics to app.py 
4. configure database
5. create model for your app
6. create routes for GET and POST
7. create a templates folder and define html files as per need
8. create view to get the data details
9. create static folder for css
10. go to terminal and python console
11. initiate database

